query:
INSERT INTO
                recursion_tip_witness_jobs_fri (
                    l1_batch_number,
                    status,
                    number_of_final_node_jobs,
                    created_at,
                    updated_at
                )
            VALUES
                ($1, 'waiting_for_proofs', 1, NOW(), NOW()) ON CONFLICT (l1_batch_number) DO
            UPDATE
            SET
                status = $2
